{"id":2602,"date":"2025-05-13T15:57:28","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:57:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2602"},"modified":"2025-06-05T13:58:45","modified_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:58:45","slug":"cach-su-dung-mat-na","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/cach-su-dung-mat-na\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c quen thu\u1ed9c. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/i><b><i> m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u skincare ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n. C\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 <\/span><\/i><b><i>c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"rua-mat-hay-khong-sau-khi-dung-mat-na-gel\"><\/span><b>R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t hay kh\u00f4ng sau khi d\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1c nhau v\u1ec1 t\u00ean con m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c. V\u1edbi m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i r\u1eeda l\u1ea1i sau khi \u0111\u1eafp kh\u00f4ng? C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00f3. M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u00edch, kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gi\u1ea5y. N\u00ean n\u1ebfu r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1, s\u0103n ch\u1eafc cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel khi kh\u00f4 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t da, gi\u00fap d\u1ec5 b\u00f3c m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ra kh\u1ecfi m\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 l\u1ed9t n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da th\u00ec da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y nh\u1ea5t \u1edf lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ee9c th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, s\u0103n ch\u1eafc. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n d\u1ea7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n nh\u1eb9. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng r\u1eeda l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t sau khi \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i \u0111a d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t, t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: Da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-buoc-su-dung-mat-na-gel-dung-cach-tai-nha\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">4 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho b\u1ea1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 &#8211; C\u00f9ng xem ngay nh\u00e9:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da: Da m\u1eb7t s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c tinh ch\u1ea5t trong m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 da lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kho\u1ebb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00eam t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft, gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc toner c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m da v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 p.H cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2605\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2605\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2605 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: \u0110\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel: Thoa l\u1edbp m\u1ecfng t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00ean tr\u00ean, tr\u00e1nh v\u00f9ng m\u1eaft, ch\u1edd 15-20 ph\u00fat\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Sau khi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y da m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4, b\u1ea1n b\u00f3c t\u1eeb t\u1eeb l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00ean. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4 nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 &#8211; \u0110i ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u00fang gi\u1edd ( tr\u01b0\u1edbc 11 gi\u1edd) \u0111\u1ec3 da x2 s\u1ef1 xinh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u00e9<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"-q-a-mot-so-cau-hoi-khi-su-dung-mat-na-nang-co-cang-bong-da\"><\/span><b>[ Q&amp;A ] M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2604\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2604\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2604 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-gel.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-gel.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-gel-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-gel-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-gel-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2604\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 &#8211; M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tan-suat-dap-mat-na-nang-co-la-bao-nhieu\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da th\u01b0\u1eddng: 3-4 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n: 2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n (\u01b0u ti\u00ean m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ea5t s\u00e9t).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: 1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, da s\u1ebd b\u1ecb &#8220;qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i&#8221; v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-diem-thich-hop-dap-mat-na-trong-ngay\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 trong ng\u00e0y?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng (8-9h): Gi\u00fap da t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i (t\u1eeb 21-22h): \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m da th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-su-dung-mat-na-%e2%80%93-su-dung-bao-lau-thi-lot\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 &#8211; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bao l\u00e2u th\u00ec l\u1ed9t?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1: Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y theo t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5m v\u00e0o da trong kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 10 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 ph\u00fat.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, n\u00e2ng c\u01a1, ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a<\/b><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"goi-y-mat-na-gel-phuc-hoi-cang-bong-da-tu-gsc\"><\/span><b>G\u1ee3i \u00fd m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da t\u1eeb GSC<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ede ph\u1ea7n tr\u00ean GSC \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho b\u1ea1n c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i \u00fd t\u1edbi b\u1ea3n 2 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 GSC nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2597 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc.webp\" alt=\"GSC M\u1eb7t N\u1ea1 N\u00e2ng C\u01a1\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-repair-control-modeling-mask\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC REPAIR CONTROL MODELING MASK<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1<\/strong> n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da GSC ch\u1ee9a tinh ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0ng 24K, l\u00e0 v\u00e0ng nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5t 100%. Kh\u00f4ng pha tr\u1ed9n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kim lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tinh khi\u1ebft t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Peptide: K\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Collagen th\u1ee7y ph\u00e2n: D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o da, gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nano v\u00e0ng 24K: Gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Collagen th\u1ee7y ph\u00e2n, 6 chu\u1ed7i peptide, amino acid: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t d\u1ea7u jojoba, hoa anh th\u1ea3o, macca, hoa t\u1ea7m xu\u00e2n: D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tripeptide-1, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-1, rau m\u00e1: Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch th\u00edch qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t collagen v\u00e0 elastin, gi\u00fap da tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng m\u00e1u, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe kho\u1eafn v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, gi\u00fap g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap da th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n t\u1ee9c th\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p tr\u00ean da. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da b\u1ea1n. GSC lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. H\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i GSC \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb9o v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 skincare chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u skincare ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n. C\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2603,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[11,12],"class_list":["post-2602","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-cham-soc-da","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2602","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2602"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2602\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3877,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2602\/revisions\/3877"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2603"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2602"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2602"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2602"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}